import React from 'react'
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid'
import Fb from 'components/Fb'
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography'
import useStyles from './styles';


const Footer = () => {
  const classes = useStyles()
  return (
      <Grid container md={12} justifyContent='center' alignItems='center' style={{background: 'rgba(13, 22, 33, 0.9)', height: '80px'}}>
        <Grid item md={2}>
          Best Hookah Store
        </Grid>
          <Grid item md={7}>
            <Fb column alignCenter>
            <Typography style={{
              fontFamily: 'Copperplate',
              fontStyle: 'normal',
              fontWeight: 'normal',
              fontSize: '24px',
              lineHeight: '25px',
            }}>
              The Capital Shop
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant='p' style={{
              fontFamily: 'Copperplate',
              fontStyle: 'normal',
              fontWeight: 'normal',
              fontSize: '12px',
              lineHeight: '12px',
            }}>
              since 2020
            </Typography>
            </Fb>
          </Grid>
        <Grid item md={2}>
          <Typography>
            +374 77 16-52-31
          </Typography>
          <Typography>
            thecapitalshop@gmail.com
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
  )
}

export default Footer
